08:11  Monday 07 September 2015  
   
Motorists face delays on the M62 this morning (Monday) after a multi-vehicle accident. 

		 
One lane is blocked on the eastbound carriageway between junction 22 for Rishworth Moor and junction 23 for Huddersfield because of a collision between two lorries and two cars. 

Traffic is queueing back to junction 21 and motorists have been told to expect delays. 

			
			 
		
		  
